{{!--
  LOGOS RIBBON
  Kinetic 3D-perspective marquee. Three-layer architecture:
    1. Section  — clipping viewport + 3D camera (perspective)
    2. Carrier  — over-wide container with rotateZ (diagonal) + rotateY (depth)
    3. Track    — flex logos, x-translated by GSAP for seamless infinite loop

  Future interaction: add [data-pullable] to any .logos-ribbon-item and wire up
  the pull-out hook at the bottom of the init script.



<section class="positioning-slide positioning-slide-main" id="helix-alt" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
